$ HTML element input (type=date)

code {
<input type="date" id="dt" name="report-date"
  value="2022-08-28"
  min="2000-01-01"
  max="2038-01-18"
/>
code }

Note, while the `value` attribute takes a date in `yyyy-mm-dd` format, the date is displayed in the browser's locale!

